Package hr.fer.zemris.java.hw11.jnotepadpp.local.swing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FormLocalizationProvider
    Modification of LocalizationProviderBridge for usage with JFrame objects.
    LocalizableAction
    This localizable AbstractAction changes its name every time the localization of the ILocalizationProvider given in the constructor is changed.
    LocalizableJLabel
    This localizable JLabel changes its text every time the localization of the ILocalizationProvider given in the constructor is changed.
    LocalizableJMenu
    This localizable JMenu changes its name every time the localization of the ILocalizationProvider given in the constructor is changed.
    LocalizableJToolbar
    This localizable JToolBar changes its name every time the localization of the ILocalizationProvider given in the constructor is changed.
